title: Quarantine Bush (feat. Justin Silver)
description: Dan & Jay pledge to grow out their man-bushes until the quarantine is lifted. Jay gives his thoughts on Feldog's motivation behind "My Truth:The Rape of Two Coreys" Documentary. Dan discusses how he will reveal the secret identity of his girlfriend to the world. DJ Lou confesses to facetime sex with his girlfriend.
